?v=1742996095 768w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/Way_to_Use_1-Lavender-purple_500x.jpg?v=1742996095 320w" width="1252" height="494" alt="Way to Use 1-Lavender-purple.jpg__PID:56e1ad9b-653a-446f-80e8-55c3a28b7b2b" data-pf-type="Image3" id="HowToUse" class="sc-gplwNw cwEcYX pf-545_ pf-image-1 pf-lg-hide"/></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-f2ea" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-djVWQC gRHrFs pf-546_ pf-color-scheme-1"><div style="--cw:850px" class="sc-ggqHwD fxhwFP"><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-547_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-djTQOc gLxCly pf-548_"><h2 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-549_ pf-heading-1-h2">LAVENDER ESSENTIAL OIL</h2><h2 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-551_ pf-heading-1-h2">How to Work It into Your Daily Routine</h2><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-553_ pf-heading-1-h3">RELAX AND UNWIND NATURALLY</h3><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-dISoPS kgxkyr pf-555_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eONOlN iAhVxb pf-556_">Aromatherapy Diffuser – Add 5–10 drops to a diffuser for a calming atmosphere.&nbsp;</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eONOlN iAhVxb pf-558_">Pillow Mist – Mix 10 drops of lavender oil with 100 ml water in a spray bottle. Spritz on your pillow before bed.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eONOlN iAhVxb pf-560_">Stress-Relief Inhalation – Put 1–2 drops on your palms, rub together, and inhale deeply.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eONOlN iAhVxb pf-562_">Relaxing Bath – Add 6–8 drops to a warm bath with a spoonful of carrier oil or Epsom salt to dissolve the oil.</li></ul><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-564_ pf-heading-1-h3">SUPPORT FOR SKIN CARE &amp; EVERYDAY FIRST AID</h3><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-dISoPS kgxkyr pf-566_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eONOlN iAhVxb pf-567_">Burns &amp; Cuts – Apply 1 drop neat (undiluted) to minor burns or cuts for quick healing.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eONOlN iAhVxb pf-569_">Acne &amp; Blemishes – Mix 1 drop with 1 tsp Aloe Vera and dab on pimples.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eONOlN iAhVxb pf-571_">Bug Bites &amp; Itchy Skin – Apply 1 drop directly to bites or mix with coconut oil.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eONOlN iAhVxb pf-573_">Sunburn Relief – Mix 5 drops with aloe vera gel and apply to sunburned skin.</li></ul><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-575_ pf-heading-1-h3">SOOTHE MUSCLE TENTION &amp; EASE DISCOMFORT</h3><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-dISoPS kgxkyr pf-577_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eONOlN iAhVxb pf-578_">Headache Relief – Rub 1–2 drops on temples, neck, or behind ears.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eONOlN iAhVxb pf-580_">Muscle &amp; Joint Pain – Mix 5 drops with 1 tbsp carrier oil (e.g., coconut, almond) and massage onto sore areas.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eONOlN iAhVxb pf-582_">Menstrual Cramp Relief – Mix with a carrier oil and massage onto the lower abdomen.</li></ul><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-584_ pf-heading-1-h3">BREATHE EASY WITH NATURAL RESPIRATORY SUPPORT</h3><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-dISoPS kgxkyr pf-586_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eONOlN iAhVxb pf-587_">Cold &amp; Congestion Steam Inhalation – Add 3–5 drops to hot water, cover your head with a towel, and inhale deeply.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eONOlN iAhVxb pf-589_">Cough &amp; Throat Relief – Mix 2 drops with carrier oil and rub on the chest and throat.</li></ul><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-591_ pf-heading-1-h3">FRESHEN YOUR HOME AND SIMPLIFY YOUR ROUTINE</h3><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-dISoPS kgxkyr pf-593_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eONOlN iAhVxb pf-594_">	Natural Room Freshener – Add 10 drops to a spray bottle with water and mist around your home.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eONOlN iAhVxb pf-596_">Laundry Freshener – Add 5 drops to a damp washcloth and toss it into the dryer.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eONOlN iAhVxb pf-598_">Natural Cleaning – Add 10 drops to a spray bottle with vinegar and water for a disinfecting cleaner.</li></ul><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-600_ pf-heading-1-h3">GENTE &amp; CALMING FOR KIDS AND BABIES</h3><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-dISoPS kgxkyr pf-602_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eONOlN iAhVxb pf-603_">	Colic Relief – Mix 1 drop with 1 tbsp carrier oil and massage onto baby’s tummy.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eONOlN iAhVxb pf-605_">Calm Fussy Babies – Diffuse 2 drops in a room before bedtime.</li></ul></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-9374" data-pf-type="Section" id="Skin" class="sc-djVWQC gRHrFs pf-607_ pf-color-scheme-1"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-ggqHwD fxhwFP"><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-608_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-djTQOc gLxCly pf-609_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/Pflanzenstrich_blau.png?v=1711454056" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/Pflanzenstrich_blau.png?v=1711454056 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/Pflanzenstrich_blau_1000x.png?v=1711454056 768w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/Pflanzenstrich_blau_500x.png?v=1711454056 320w" width="3514" height="230" alt="Pflanzenstrich_blau.png__PID:b850d7e1-c00f-4273-9b83-e2ecbfbe7683" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-gplwNw cwEcYX pf-610_ pf-image-1"/></div></div></div><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-611_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-djTQOc gLxCly pf-612_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/780x370_pictures_pamper3.jpg?v=1742998723" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/780x370_pictures_pamper3.jpg?v=1742998723 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/780x370_pictures_pamper3_1000x.jpg?v=1742998723 768w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/780x370_pictures_pamper3_500x.jpg?v=1742998723 320w" width="780" height="370" alt="780x370 pictures pamper3.jpg__PID:5e932e16-b73a-41d6-831a-dcb858b81bbe" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-gplwNw cwEcYX pf-613_ pf-image-1"/></div></