-1 pf-md-hide pf-sm-hide pf-hide"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-ggqHwD fxhwFP"><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-640_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-djTQOc gLxCly pf-641_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/Pflanzenstrich_blau.png?v=1711454056" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/Pflanzenstrich_blau.png?v=1711454056 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/Pflanzenstrich_blau_1000x.png?v=1711454056 768w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/Pflanzenstrich_blau_500x.png?v=1711454056 320w" width="3514" height="230" alt="Pflanzenstrich_blau.png__PID:b850d7e1-c00f-4273-9b83-e2ecbfbe7683" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-gplwNw cwEcYX pf-642_ pf-image-1"/><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-643_ pf-heading-1-h3">DIY recipes with Lavender Oils and Hydrolates</h3></div></div></div><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-645_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:4;--c-lg:4"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-djTQOc gLxCly pf-646_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/600x400_spray_bottle_laavender.jpg?v=1743418096" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/600x400_spray_bottle_laavender.jpg?v=1743418096 1536w" width="600" height="400" alt="600x400 spray bottle laavender.jpg__PID:e1b729e3-1443-41db-a75e-683689fa3213" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-gplwNw cwEcYX pf-647_ pf-image-1"/><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-648_ pf-heading-1-h3">Dreamy&nbsp;Pillow Spray</h3><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-650_ pf-heading-1-h3">Perfect for relaxation and better sleep!</h3><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-652_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">The Good Stuff </p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-dISoPS kgxkyr pf-654_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eONOlN iAhVxb pf-655_">¼  cup Lavender Hydrolate</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eONOlN iAhVxb pf-657_">5 drops Lavender Essential Oil</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eONOlN iAhVxb pf-659_">1 tbsp Witch Hazel (helps mix the oil)</li></ul><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-661_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Mix &amp; Enjoy</p><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-663_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Pour all the ingredients into a spray bottle and give it a good shake. Before bedtime, shake well and mist lightly over your pillow and bedding. Breathe in, relax, and drift into dreamland!</p></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:4;--c-lg:4"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-djTQOc gLxCly pf-665_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/600x400_body_butter.jpg?v=1743415696" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/600x400_body_butter.jpg?v=1743415696 1536w" width="600" height="400" alt="600x400 body butter.jpg__PID:e366c6e1-1228-4a0b-881f-63727cef18a5" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-gplwNw cwEcYX pf-666_ pf-image-1"/><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-667_ pf-heading-1-h3">&nbsp;Lavender Body Butter</h3><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-669_ pf-heading-1-h3">Deeply Moisturizes And Soothes The Skin!</h3><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-671_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">&nbsp;the good stuff</p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-dISoPS kgxkyr pf-673_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eONOlN iAhVxb pf-674_">½ cup Shea Butter</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eONOlN iAhVxb pf-676_">¼ cup Coconut Oil</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eONOlN iAhVxb pf-678_">10 drops Lavender Essential Oil</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eONOlN iAhVxb pf-680_">1 tsp Vitamin E Oil</li></ul><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-682_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Mix &amp; Enjoy</p><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-684_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Melt the shea butter and coconut oil together in a double boiler. Let it cool until it’s just slightly firm, then whip it up with a hand mixer. Add in your lavender oil and vitamin E, and give it another whip. Store in a glass jar and use whenever your skin needs a little love!</p></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:4;--c-lg:4"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-djTQOc gLxCly pf-686_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/600x400_bath_salt.jpg?v=1743418587" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/600x400_bath_salt.jpg?v=1743418587 1536w" width="600" height="400" alt="600x400 bath salt.jpg__PID:2cc77a33-6192-404f-b59e-bf8db97745b3" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-gplwNw cwEcYX pf-687_ pf-image-1"/><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-688_ pf-heading-1-h3"> Relaxation Bath Salt</h3><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-690_ pf-heading-1-h3">Ideal for stress relief and tired muscles!</h3><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-692_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">The Good Stuff </p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-dISoPS kgxkyr pf-694_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eONOlN iAhVxb pf-695_">1 cup Epsom Salt</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eONOlN iAhVxb pf-697_">	½ cup Sea Salt</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eONOlN iAhVxb pf-699_">10 drops of Lavender Essential Oil</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eONOlN iAhVxb pf-701_">1 tbsp  Baking Soda (softens water)</li></ul><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-703_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Mix &amp; Enjoy</p><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-705_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Combine all the ingredients in a jar and give it a little shake. When you're ready to unwind, add ¼ cup to a warm bath, sink in, and let the soothing aroma melt your stress away!</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-707_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:4;--c-lg:4"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-djTQOc gLxCly pf-708_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/600x400_face_sprays3.jpg?v=1743502365" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/600x400_face_sprays3.jpg?v=1743502365 1536w" width="600" height="400" alt="600x400 face sprays3.jpg__PID:7f104452-ab85-4924-be56-543cb5cb7fbb" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-gplwNw cwEcYX pf-709_ pf-image-1"/><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-710_ pf-heading-1-h3">Soothing Face Mist </h3><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-712_ pf-heading-1-h3">Hydrates and refreshes naturally!</h3><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-714_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">The Good Stuff </p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-dISoPS kgxkyr pf-716_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eONOlN iAhVxb pf-717_">¼  cup of&nbsp;Lavender Hydrolate</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eONOlN iAhVxb pf-719_">1 tsp&nbsp;Aloe Vera Gel</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eONOlN iAhVxb pf-721_">3 drops of Lavender Essential Oil</li></ul><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-723_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Mix &amp; Enjoy</p><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-725_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Mix all your ingredients in a spray bottle and give it a good shake.&nbsp;Whenever you need a refresh, mist it lightly&nbsp; it onto your face for a burst of hydration and a soothing, cooling feel.</p></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:4;--c-lg:4"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-djTQOc gLxCly pf-727_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/600x400_headache_oil_312bed99-d9d5-4bab-bfe3-34691b276ae7.jpg?v=1743499454" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/600x400_headache_oil_312bed99-d9d5-4bab-bfe3-34691b276ae7.jpg?v=1743499454 1536w" width="600" height="400" alt="600x400 headache oil.jpg__PID:d29fbf33-9414-4c8c-b523-ff51d972d4a0" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-gplwNw cwEcYX pf-728_ pf-image-1"/><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-729_ pf-heading-1-h3">Headache &amp; Stress Relief &nbsp;</h3><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-731_ pf-heading-1-h3 pf-hide">Eases headaches and calms your mind.</h3><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-733_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">The Good Stuff </p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-dISoPS kgxkyr pf-735_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eONOlN iAhVxb pf-736_">2&nbsp;tsp&nbsp;Jojoba or Almond Oil&nbsp;</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eONOlN iAhVxb pf-738_">5 drops of Lavender Essential Oil</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eONOlN iAhVxb pf-740_">3 drops Peppermint Essential Oil</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eONOlN iAhVxb pf-742_">1 roller bottle</li></ul><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-744_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Mix &amp; Enjoy</p><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-746_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Mix all the ingredients in your roll-on bottle. Once it’s all set, just roll it onto your temples, wrists, and behind your ears whenever you need a little relief. This soothing blend helps calm tension headaches and gets you into full relaxation mode.</p></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:4;--c-lg:4"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-djTQOc gLxCly pf-748_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/600x400_cleaning_sprays2.jpg?v=1743502122" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0567/2563/5262/files/600x400_cleaning_sprays2.jpg?v=1743502122 1536w" width="600" height="400" alt="600x400 cleaning sprays2.jpg__PID:731a3a3d-a1f1-4674-bb18-f8b4f5eb856c" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-gplwNw cwEcYX pf-749_ pf-image-1"/><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-750_ pf-heading-1-h3"> All-Purpose Cleaner </h3><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-752_ pf-heading-1-h3">A natural, antibacterial home cleaner!</h3><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-754_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">The Good Stuff </p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-dISoPS kgxkyr pf-756_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eONOlN iAhVxb pf-757_">1 cup White Vinegar</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eONOlN iAhVxb pf-759_">&nbsp;1 cup Water</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eONOlN iAhVxb pf-761_">10 drops of Lavender Essential Oil</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eONOlN iAhVxb pf-763_">&nbsp;5 drops Tea Tree Essential Oil</li></ul><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-765_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Mix &amp; Enjoy</p><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-767_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Mix everything in a spray bottle, shake it up, and get spritzing! Perfect for wiping down kitchen counters, bathroom sinks, and all those messy spots—plus, it leaves your space smelling like a dreamy lavender field. Who knew cleaning could feel this good and natural?</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-769_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-djTQOc gLxCly pf-770_"><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-771_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Sources (1): <a href="https://pmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/articles/PMC5437114/?utm_source=chatgpt.com" target="_blank">https://pmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/articles/PMC9886818</a><a href="https://pmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/articles/PMC5437114/?utm_source=chatgpt.com" target="_blank">/</a> ;&nbsp;<a href="https://pmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/articles/PMC9886818/" target="_blank">https://pmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/articles/PMC9886818/</a> ; <a href="https://pmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/articles/PMC3521421/?utm_source=chatgpt.com" target="_blank">https://pmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/articles/PMC3521421/; https://pmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/articles/PMC5437114</a>/ ; <a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/26247152/" target="_blank">https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/262471</a><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/26247152/" target="_self"></a>52/ ; <a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/17689755/" target="_blank">https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/17689755/<br><br>Sources (2):  Koulivand, P. H., Faridi, P., &amp; Afshari, R. (2013). Lavender and the nervous system: A review of its clinical effects and potential mechanisms of action. The Journal of Alternative and Complementary Medicine, 19(5), 349-356. • Doherty, A., &amp; McGee, M. (2004). Lavender oil as an adjunctive therapy for insomnia and anxiety. The International Journal of Neuroscience, 114(10), 1259-1265. •